description:
Favourite Foods for Dogs PLUS! is the first ever dog catalog of over 160+ dog breeds for HP WebOS! 

The PLUS version provides different types of dog breeds accompanied with its videos, origins, nicknames, pictures, characteristics and best of all its favorite foods! 

We have surveyed over 100 dog owners for each specific dog breed to find out what their breed's favourite foods are! 

If you have a pet dog, this app is no doubt a-must-be-owned in your WebOS devices. 

You can also use this application to look through different type of breeds and help you decide on your future or new pet dog! 

If you have any other breeds that are not listed, you can visit our website support and we will get another round of surveys and update the app! 

Enjoy!
